Attribution

@aberhamm/liquid-glass-react is an independent reimplementation of the
liquid-glass UI technique popularized by the following projects, both
distributed under the MIT License:

  - rdev/liquid-glass-react   (https://github.com/rdev/liquid-glass-react)
  - shuding/liquid-glass      (https://github.com/shuding/liquid-glass)

This project draws inspiration from the prop surface, naming, and visual intent
of those works, but is a clean-room reimplementation: no source code was copied
from either project. This attribution is provided to acknowledge that lineage
and to affirm the independent, non-fork nature of this implementation. It does
not imply endorsement by the original authors.
